text: Novokulevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Novokulevsky Selsoviet, Nurimanovsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,465 as of 2010. There are 28 streets. == Geography == It is located 15 km from Krasnaya Gorka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Nurimanovsky District
title: Novokulevo
